content: HashWarlock: Merged 4 PRs this week, including significant feature work with the addition of redpill support (#4045, +773/-5 lines) and TEE CI/CD pipeline implementation (#3994, +1689/-957 lines), alongside important fixes for the plugin-TEE system (#3982, +1295/-941 lines) and removal of TEE logs (#3966, +14/-1050 lines). Active on 4 days with a balanced focus between bugfixes (38%) and feature development (25%), resulting in modifications to 33 files across 8 commits.
